with oneself and

00:01:15.060 --> 00:01:16.840 align:middle line:90%
with the natural surroundings.

00:01:16.840 --> 00:01:17.640 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:01:17.640 --> 00:01:19.380 align:middle line:84%
