a smile on their face

00:02:44.970 --> 00:02:46.180 align:middle line:10%
as they're feeling the pulses.

00:02:46.180 --> 00:02:46.830 align:middle line:90%
>> Isn't that amazing?

00:02:46.830 --> 00:02:47.630 align:middle line:90%
>> Literally.

00:02:47.630 --> 00:02:50.240 align:middle line:84%
