00:02:50.240 --> 00:02:51.040 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, no.

00:02:51.040 --> 00:02:51.310 align:middle line:90%
I'm a believer.

00:02:51.310 --> 00:02:51.760 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:02:51.760 --> 00:02:52.015 align:middle line:90%
>> Great.

00:02:52.015 --> 00:02:52.270 align:middle line:90%
Great.

00:02:52.270 --> 00:02:53.812 align:middle line:84%
