00:03:07.280 --> 00:03:08.730 align:middle line:90%
I laugh at myself every day.

00:03:08.730 --> 00:03:09.530 align:middle line:90%
>> [LAUGHS]

00:03:09.530 --> 00:03:12.510 align:middle line:84%
