00:03:18.810 --> 00:03:19.170 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:03:19.170 --> 00:03:20.023 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, exactly.

00:03:20.023 --> 00:03:21.440 align:middle line:84%
>> That awful thing
