00:11:54.207 --> 00:11:56.290 align:middle line:84%
And she pulled out a little
black case of needles.

00:11:56.290 --> 00:11:58.270 align:middle line:84%
And I don't remember
exactly, but she put them

00:11:58.270 --> 00:12:00.270 align:middle line:84%
somewhere near the thumbs
and near his big toes.

00:12:00.270 --> 00:12:01.070 align:middle line:90%
>> Wow.

00:12:01.070 --> 00:12:03.700 align:middle line:84%
>> And within two minutes,
he was up and around and back

00:12:03.700 --> 00:12:05.020 align:middle line:90%
to his old self.

00:12:05.020 --> 00:12:06.670 align:middle line:84%
>> Now, we also have
an example here.

00:12:06.670 --> 00:12:08.500 align:middle line:84%
And they are little,
and they are tiny.

00:12:08.500 --> 00:12:10.330 align:middle line:84%
And you said that we
could just kind of

00:12:10.330 --> 00:12:14.340 align:middle line:84%
see this is what the needle's
actually encapsulated in.

00:12:14.340 --> 00:12:16.270 align:middle line:84%
So it is a tiny
little needle, but it

00:12:16.270 --> 00:12:19.630 align:middle line:84%
is a powerful little needle
then, too, is it not?

00:12:19.630 --> 00:12:22.900 align:middle line:84%
>> The typical acupuncture
needle is about an inch long

00:12:22.900 --> 00:12:25.150 align:middle line:84%
and about the diameter
of a human hair.

00:12:25.150 --> 00:12:28.130 align:middle line:84%
Most people have visions
of hypodermic needles.

00:12:28.130 --> 00:12:30.650 align:middle line:84%
And they don't even
want to come see you.

00:12:30.650 --> 00:12:32.878 align:middle line:84%
Because a lot of people
this needle phobia.

00:12:32.878 --> 00:12:34.420 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, we're going
