seen Tai Chi done,

00:15:07.930 --> 00:15:10.270 align:middle line:84%
and they have-- some
have seen qigong.

00:15:10.270 --> 00:15:16.560 align:middle line:84%
And what we note about it,
it is in very slow motion.

00:15:16.560 --> 00:15:17.360 align:middle line:90%
OK?

00:15:17.360 --> 00:15:18.190 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:15:18.190 --> 00:15:21.650 align:middle line:84%
